  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/3e2d14e643829bfd20349467d6edaf5c.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/3e2d14e643829bfd20349467d6edaf5c.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter an unusual 1960s office, trapped in a loop. In this 1-6 player co-op or single-player adventure, you'll explore rooms 0 to 9, where anomalies may appear in some rooms but not all. Objects shift, disappear, or appear where they don’t belong, and it’s up to you to find them. Solve puzzles, avoid deadly traps, and find all anomalies to progress. The eerie atmosphere keeps you on edge, with each room bringing you closer to the exit—or sending you back to Room 0.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/d5ed036f843163e82c62bd30b56693cc.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/d5ed036f843163e82c62bd30b56693cc.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/505e0fdbd11e6f861ff08aa6e271077c.poster.avif?t=1772735293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/505e0fdbd11e6f861ff08aa6e271077c.webm?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/505e0fdbd11e6f861ff08aa6e271077c.mp4?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Start at Room 0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>No Anomalies in Room 0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>In each Room, something may be different from Room 0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Mark the differences as anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>If you mark the anomalies correctly you will move to the next level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>If you're wrong you will go back to Room 0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Exit at Room 9</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Online Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Explore an online multiplayer experience for 1-6 players, working together to find anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Players can join or host lobbies, either private or public</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Communicate and help each other through text chat or in-game</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Single Player</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Explore the single-player experience, identical to the multiplayer mode</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Equipments</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mark tool</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>A simple tool to mark anomalies. Use it to mark, undo, or clear all marks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Play together with 1-6 players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Immerse yourself in atmospheric places</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Find and mark anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Solve puzzles to proceed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>Be careful of deadly traps</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/a0bf5ba40cd21eec8dc748adccfddaab.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/a0bf5ba40cd21eec8dc748adccfddaab.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/234df9d1b6a60a03fb67aea519f12577.poster.avif?t=1772735293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/234df9d1b6a60a03fb67aea519f12577.webm?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/234df9d1b6a60a03fb67aea519f12577.mp4?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, there are 9 rooms. Each one is like Room 0 (the starting room), but with some changes, like objects being replaced, changed, or new ones appearing. These changes are called anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/d29142ff8870837e59954b9bddcb24a2.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/d29142ff8870837e59954b9bddcb24a2.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Observation Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/134c53c44dea673bf809cd05f3e1eae0.poster.avif?t=1772735293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/134c53c44dea673bf809cd05f3e1eae0.webm?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/134c53c44dea673bf809cd05f3e1eae0.mp4?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 unique anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short Story:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Observation Room was originally created to study the endless expanse of Black Water, a mysterious, pitch-black sea full of anomalies and strange occurrences. At first, it was a place for careful observation, but soon, these anomalies began to appear inside the room itself. What started as small changes gradually escalated, with objects in the room shifting, dangerous new items appearing, and deadly traps materializing where they didn’t belong. Now, a team is assigned every morning to find and mark all anomalies from Room 0 to 9, and then exit, identifying their frequency to return them to their original state or eliminate non-existent objects — today, it’s your team's turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and mark all anomalies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Platform Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/6e859c842db1b31a887f057134fed7ee.poster.avif?t=1772735293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/6e859c842db1b31a887f057134fed7ee.webm?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/6e859c842db1b31a887f057134fed7ee.mp4?t=1772735293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>80 unique anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short Story:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for one purpose: trapping and studying anomalies. Teams manage four monitor-equipped cubicles to control the central Sealed Chamber, a high-security prison where captured entities are imprisoned for analysis. Mark the distortions and keep them locked away at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and mark all anomalies!<strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/d6646b03274df30bf536c564b5e83c28.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/d6646b03274df30bf536c564b5e83c28.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in an unusual 1960s office, the environment is built using Unreal Engine 5 to create a uniquely chilling experience. Cinematic lighting, details, and thoughtful design create a tense and unsettling atmosphere. With horror and gore elements, Exit Together hides many surprises that keep players on edge. The mix of retro style and modern graphics adds to the thriller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras/e8812a0e24c143a0fce26e8ea5a50ff6.avif?t=1772735293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333740/extras_big/e8812a0e24c143a0fce26e8ea5a50ff6.avif?t=1772735293 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >>All achievements can also be completed in single-player</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
